                        "utilityType":  "control",
                        "description":  "Infuse a point with holy or unholy power to create an until-dispelled area up to a 60-foot radius; the spell fails if the area overlaps another Hallow. The ward can block chosen Aberration, Celestial, Elemental, Fey, Fiend, or Undead creatures from willingly entering and suppress possession, Charmed, and Frightened effects caused by them, with chosen types optionally excluded. The caster also binds one extra area effect, chosen from the spell options or a DM option; affected creatures can be filtered by creature kind, deity, or leader, and can make the listed Charisma save when entering or starting there to ignore that extra effect until they leave.",
